{"tid":1408243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[廣傳/輿論/FACT] 包圍事件起因: 警察將街坊扑到流哂血","createTime":"2019-08-04T16:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T17:01:16.000Z","uid":15696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b092b3ec66d6a55fc6e2c8cb45bcae3f6e6a2727","tid":1408243,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:52:13.000Z","msg":"聽日CCTVB一定隻字不提，請廣傳!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[輿論戰] 將軍澳老竇被打單嘢一定要搞大佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1407655/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1407655/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳 警察突發增援 打街坊打記者 拉走咗街坊嘅呀爸(呀伯)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1407377/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1407377/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tP6ved0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtP6ved0.jpg&h=f1f8f842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kTotr0ebJYk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkTotr0ebJYk&d=uztthH5CN7iuCFQPSeIHaS1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=a8860c1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kTotr0ebJYk</a>"},{"pid":"51466d6d4bd8e69fb7bc1e27753b8331791dacb1","tid":1408243,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:53:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夫無啦啦一個街坊市民手無寸鐵食完飯散步行公園都要俾警察兜頭扑<br />\n打到流晒血記者發現即刻推記者走<br />\n攞強光電筒照住鏡頭<br />\n個仔要去睇佢爸爸又比啲狗阻鳩住<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁樣係公然阻礙新聞自由同埋濫用私刑<br />\n<br />\n陳生一家一定要告佢！<br />\n搵返負責任嘅狗，要佢哋接受法律嘅制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/dXmGkQS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXmGkQS.png&h=94c6ccac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/E1wZRXD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE1wZRXD.png&h=80bd2e7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/AJ4s0Q6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAJ4s0Q6.png&h=e9c442eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"db0d1af6c2ed24bf7f51d93c74c08b460966665e","tid":1408243,"uid":260793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7d095012a25ac8dd859a3b8fcf2da81a301331","tid":1408243,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:54:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>速龍打完佢仲要話佢自己跌傷<br />\n陳生即刻對住記者澄清係速龍拎警棍打佢後腦<br />\n又阻住個仔見老豆</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4d58394db98dcb17dddf8680f2ccd8f14fd37fed","tid":1408243,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:54:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港警察<br />\n扑鳩市民</span>"},{"pid":"fea527b685ace68f7c07c37e585085ff88927c86","tid":1408243,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:56:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">街坊可能又會被捕+開記招譴責<br />\n如果聽日有港豬屌街坊，請廣傳包圍事件起因</span>"},{"pid":"19fc686fc36c7f1154791ddfb4d2ea89257e331d","tid":1408243,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:56:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">討回公道</span>"},{"pid":"8877d4b980ee91a5a2dd7b860782558cca19916c","tid":1408243,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:58:09.000Z","msg":"CCTVB員工你仲有冇良心?"},{"pid":"f4c1b3ecd3395b5d7d6122157a1f5ab097cf33b2","tid":1408243,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/KYcVqGf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%